Instructions are for Mac System
export DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/Oracle_DB-XML/dbxml-2.5.16/install/lib/

Instructions are for Linux System
LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/Oracle_DB_XML/dbxml-2.5.16/install/lib
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH

In order for JBoss to pick the required changes add
-Djava.library.path=/opt/OracleBDB-XML/dbxml-2.5.16/install/lib/

to appropriate script. 
For JBoss 7 it is standalone.sh or domain.sh. 

